Description: High-performance NGINX with QUIC/HTTP3 and extra modules
 NGINX built from latest sources with QUIC and HTTP/3 support,
 packaged as a Debian .deb for easy installation and updates.
 .
 Extra modules included:
  - ngx_brotli (Google Brotli compression)
  - headers-more (OpenResty headers-more module)
  - njs (NGINX JavaScript)
  - zstd (Zstandard compression)
  - QuickJS runtime
